ED_Title: Maintenance of international  security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe
ED_DecisionText: At its 43rd plenary meeting, on 2 December 2024, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee, (Footnote: A/79/402, para.7.)  decided to include in the provisional agenda of its eighty-first session the item entitled “Maintenance of international security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe”.
